snippet.title: DARK DECEPTION: MONSTERS & MORTALS - POPPY PLAYTIME PANIC DLC OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
The Poppy Playtime Panic DLC is now available on Steam (and coming soon to Epic Game Store)! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1825942/Monsters__Mortals__Poppy_Playtime_Panic_DLC/
The base Monsters & Mortals game is required to play all DLCs:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1266690/Dark_Deception_Monsters__Mortals/

Original Poppy Playtime tracks by:  Zachary Preciado
Monsters & Mortals cover music by: Daniel Dombrowsky
Video Editing by: Vincent Livings

Dark Deception: Monsters & Mortals ©2020-2023 Glowstick Entertainment, Inc. Developed by Glowstick Entertainment, Inc. Dark Deception and all related characters, their distinctive likenesses, and related elements are trademarks and material protected by copyright of Glowstick Entertainment, Inc. ©2023. All Rights Reserved.

Poppy Playtime’s Playtime Co. appears courtesy of Mob Entertainment, Inc. and has been reimagined for fans of Monsters & Mortals. © 2023 Mob Entertainment, Inc. All rights reserved. Poppy Playtime and related trademarks are the property of Mob Entertainment, Inc.
